title: Maria Bamford | Unaired Exclusive
description:
On March 12, 2020, comedian Maria Bamford joined Stephen Colbert in an empty Ed Sullivan Theater for a conversation about the fears they were facing at that moment of uncertainty as the impact of the global pandemic was starting to be felt in New York City.
